  <brief_title>Post-Operative Pain Scores and Analgesic Requirements After Elective Inguinal Herniorrhaphy</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Investigation of Post-Operative Pain Scores and Analgesic Requirements After Ambulatory Inguinal Herniorrhaphy With Pre-Operative Gabapentin Therapy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
