  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study will investigate the effects of single dose pre-operative oral dose of gabapentin
      (1200) on post -operative pain scores and oral analgesic requirements.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The study will benefit patients in reducing post-operative pain scores as well as reduction
      in oral analgesic consumption. Gabapentin has been shown to reduce post operative pain pain
      scores in breast surgery, hysterectomy , spinal surgery, orthopedic and thyroid surgery
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
